Package: Scad
Title: SCAD Penalized Regression using LQA and Improved Algorithms
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mengfan", "Long", email = "mengfanl@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Mengfan Long [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Mengfan Long <mengfanl@umich.edu>
Description: Implements SCAD (Smoothly Clipped Absolute Deviation) penalized 
    regression using Local Quadratic Approximation (LQA) and improved stabilized 
    algorithms (LQA with QR/SVD decomposition and adaptive ridge). Also includes 
    Dynamic SCAD model for time-varying coefficient regression with SCAD sparsity 
    penalty and temporal smoothness constraint.
